snippet.title: Bzzzt
snippet.description:
Free demoversion is available now!
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1293170/Bzzzt/

Bzzzt is a fast-paced 2D platformer highly inspired by games from 80's. You become an artificial intelligence ZX8000 and in your newly obtained robotic body, you must prove your abilities in a series of testing chambers filled with deadly traps.
